77
00:06:40,340 --> 00:06:43,720
- Sir, look at this blood. 
 - I get it. Sit down first.

78
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:48,400
- This is all because you—
 - All right, sit! Sit down.

79
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:52,010
It was not like Tateishi-san to throw a punch.

80
00:06:52,830 --> 00:06:56,030
Haruto bought us time.

81
00:06:57,720 --> 00:07:00,230
-  Sir, look at this blood. 
 - I get it. 

82
00:07:00,230 --> 00:07:02,830
-  I will not settle this out of court. 
 - Calm down. Okay? 

83
00:07:02,830 --> 00:07:05,990
-  This is your fault, Inaba!  
 - Right, we hear you. 

84
00:07:05,990 --> 00:07:10,090
-  He may have broken my nose! 
 - No, it's not broken. 

85
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:19,680
