103
00:09:48,420 --> 00:09:52,840
but I won't pester you anymore. Just rest for today.

104
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:55,040
I will.

105
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:57,250
Ouch!

106
00:10:02,680 --> 00:10:04,470
Hello?

107
00:10:04,470 --> 00:10:05,910
Hey.

108
00:10:05,910 --> 00:10:07,870
 What's up? 

109
00:10:07,870 --> 00:10:10,910
I need to ask you for a favor.

110
00:10:10,910 --> 00:10:14,710
Now it's unusual for you to ask me for a favor, Ren.

111
00:10:14,710 --> 00:10:16,090
What do you need?

112
00:10:16,090 --> 00:10:21,520
You were looking into various women involved with Inaba, right?

113
00:10:22,260 --> 00:10:24,310
I want you to pass that information to me.

114
00:10:27,800 --> 00:10:30,070
You'll owe me one.

115
00:10:31,300 --> 00:10:34,480
I know.

116
00:10:35,580 --> 00:10:38,360
Then I'll look forward to my reward.

117
00:11:51,500 --> 00:11:55,250
Tateishi-san?

118
00:11:55,250 --> 00:11:57,170
You're awake.

119
00:11:57,170 --> 00:11:59,130
Yoneda-san, it's me, Ren.

120
00:11:59,130 --> 00:12:00,670
Can you recognize me?

121
00:12:00,670 --> 00:12:03,650
Ren-san...

122
00:12:03,650 --> 00:12:06,810
And Sakura-san too...

123
00:12:06,810 --> 00:12:08,140
Thank goodness...

124
00:12:08,140 --> 00:12:11,300
Do you know who I am?

125
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:15,350
Shinjo.

126
00:12:16,100 --> 00:12:18,960
