- Was it? 
 - Yes.

142
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:55,020
Did you want to bathe first?

143
00:13:55,020 --> 00:13:57,000
No, you ought to go first, Sakura.

144
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:59,200
