148
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:44,060
Okay.

149
00:14:44,060 --> 00:14:46,650
R-Right.

150
00:14:46,650 --> 00:14:49,050
It was a long day.

151
00:14:51,790 --> 00:14:55,050
You can leave that behind.

152
00:14:55,050 --> 00:14:58,980
- It's fine. 
 - No, I'll handle it.

153
00:14:59,780 --> 00:15:02,830
